## 5. External Clients

### Axios Pattern

```typescript
const response = await axios.get<RPLaunch[]>(url, {
  headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` },
  timeout: 30_000,
});
return response.data;
```

- Type Axios responses: `axios.get<ResponseType>(url)`
- Set timeouts on ALL external requests
- Handle specific error codes (401 = re-auth, 429 = rate limit, 5xx = retry)
- Wrap in try/catch, log failures, throw typed errors

### Client Organization

- One file per external service: `clients/reportportal.ts`, `clients/jira.ts`
- Export typed functions, not the Axios instance
- Centralize auth header construction

